276
00:21:08,125 --> 00:21:10,708
<i>It'd been three weeks
since you'd seen your brother?</i>

277
00:21:10,708 --> 00:21:12,833
<i>Is that strange?</i>

278
00:21:12,833 --> 00:21:16,375
<i>When was the last time
you saw your brother?</i>

279
00:21:16,375 --> 00:21:17,625
<i>I don't have one.</i>

280
00:21:17,625 --> 00:21:19,708
<i>Well, your family then,
your mother, father,</i>

281
00:21:19,708 --> 00:21:22,250
<i>wife.</i>

282
00:21:22,250 --> 00:21:24,333
Smart. Turning it around on me.
