00:21:33,375 --> 00:21:35,750
<i>...your family,
your wife.</i>

288
00:21:36,833 --> 00:21:39,625
<i>Was she very close with your brother?</i>

289
00:21:41,083 --> 00:21:42,291
<i>Not really.</i>

