293
00:21:48,208 --> 00:21:51,000
But he's got everything
a man could possibly want.

294
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:53,625
Money, power, a beautiful wife.

295
00:21:53,625 --> 00:21:55,625
If anyone would've been jealous,
