326
00:23:37,625 --> 00:23:41,916
<i>I didn't come from money, so I had to
work my ass off to get a scholarship.</i>

327
00:23:42,916 --> 00:23:44,416
Anything else?

328
00:23:44,416 --> 00:23:46,291
