00:26:45,208 --> 00:26:46,375
Right?

376
00:26:46,375 --> 00:26:48,250
Yeah.

377
00:26:57,125 --> 00:26:59,875
<i>Digging into other people's pain...</i>

378
00:27:02,291 --> 00:27:05,750
<i>...I could somehow put
