415
00:29:46,625 --> 00:29:48,041
But, um...

416
00:29:49,416 --> 00:29:50,625
...Leo was strong.

417
00:29:50,625 --> 00:29:51,916
He had endurance.

418
00:29:51,916 --> 00:29:55,791
He could, um, stay the course, yeah?

419
00:29:55,791 --> 00:29:57,375
