killing his own brother?

445
00:31:18,125 --> 00:31:20,625
I may not like him,
but I-I don't think he's capable of that.

446
00:31:20,625 --> 00:31:23,375
If-if Leo threatened Elias...

447
00:31:23,375 --> 00:31:26,041
You said yourself Leo didn't like
