♪ ♪

1048
01:26:58,333 --> 01:27:01,291
<i>I like to think of myself as free.</i>

1049
01:27:03,583 --> 01:27:05,583
<i>But I'm not sure that's right.</i>

1050
01:27:07,125 --> 01:27:09,166
<i>I'm as caught up as anyone.</i>

1051
01:27:15,166 --> 01:27:16,708
<i>But right then...</i>

1052
01:27:18,875 --> 01:27:21,916
<i>...I was tired of flying into the sun.</i>

